OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FFamilies of the 29 people killed in
OL,7,Fthe 1994 Mull of Kintyre Chinook crash
OL,8,Fhave accused the Ministry of Defence
OL,9,F(MoD) of a "callous disregard" for
OL,10,Ftheir personal data after sensitive
OL,11,Finformation was released.
OL,13,FThe material, which was disclosed to a
OL,14,Fmedia organisation following a freedom
OL,15,Fof information (FOI) request, is said
OL,16,Fto contain sensitive personal,
OL,17,Ffinancial and legal information
OL,18,Frelating to the bereaved families.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FThe Chinook Justice Campaign, set up
OL,7,Fby the families, has now lodged a
OL,8,Fformal complaint demanding the MoD
OL,9,Frefers itself to the Information
OL,10,FCommissioner's Office.
OL,12,FThe group has demanded an urgent
OL,13,Fexplanation from ministers.
OL,15,FLawyers for the families have also
OL,16,Fcalled for the relevant documents to
OL,17,Fbe retracted and for all recipients to
OL,18,Fbe notified that the personal data
OL,19,Fshould not be published or disclosed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FMark Stephens, a human rights lawyer
OL,7,Facting for the families, said: "This
OL,8,Frepresents a serious failure to
OL,9,Fprotect the rights of families who
OL,10,Fhave been deceived and lied to from
OL,11,Fday one.
OL,13,F"It shows a callous disregard for
OL,14,Ftheir personal information, has added
OL,15,Ftrauma to a three-decade-long fight
OL,16,Ffor the truth, and raises fundamental
OL,17,Fquestions about the department's
OL,18,Fhandling of sensitive material.
OL,26,@oD@`OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,F"The Ministry of Defence must urgently
OL,7,Fexplain how and why it placed personal
OL,8,Finformation about bereaved families
OL,9,Finto the public domain without proper
OL,10,Fsafeguards or due process, or any
OL,11,Fdiscussion with those families."
OL,13,FHe said the families are "once again"
OL,14,Fbeing subjected to "further harm
OL,15,Fthrough the unlawful disclosure of
OL,16,Ftheir personal information at a time
OL,17,Fwhen the MoD claims it is engaged in
OL,18,Fdialogue with them".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@`O]uD@ZOUuD@eO]vD@TOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FHe added: "That is completely and
OL,7,Futterly unacceptable and they deserve
OL,8,Fa full and frank apology and an urgent
OL,9,Fmeeting with the Prime Minister, to
OL,10,Fwhich he has committed."
OL,12,FRAF Chinook ZD576 crashed in foggy
OL,13,Fweather while flying from RAF
OL,14,FAldergrove in Northern Ireland to Fort
OL,15,FGeorge near Inverness on June 2, 1994.
OL,17,FFor years, the pilots were wrongly
OL,18,Fblamed for the disaster before being
OL,19,Fformally cleared in 2011.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FThe Chinook Justice Campaign said an
OL,7,FFOI request by the British Forces
OL,8,FBroadcasting Service was submitted
OL,9,Fafter veterans minister Louise Sandher-
OL,10,FJones said in the House of Commons in
OL,11,FNovember that some sealed documents
OL,12,Fwere able to be requested.
OL,14,FThe families of the Chinook victims
OL,15,Fsaid the MoD had previously told them
OL,16,Fthe documents related to the disaster
OL,17,Fwere sealed for 100 years due to
OL,18,Fpersonal data reasons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FChris Cook, whose brother Flight
OL,7,FLieutenant Rick Cook was killed, said:
OL,8,F"For more than 30 years, our families
OL,9,Fhave fought for truth and
OL,10,Faccountability. For 16 of those, we
OL,11,Fhad to fight to clear Rick and Jon's
OL,12,Fnames.
OL,14,F"To now find that personal information
OL,15,Fhas been exposed in this way is deeply
OL,16,Fdistressing.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,F"It shows a complete lack of care for
OL,7,Fthe families and the impact this crash
OL,8,Fand long fight for justice has had on
OL,9,Fall of us, and is highly illustrative
OL,10,Fof the deceit and disregard we have
OL,11,Fall faced from day one.
OL,13,F"I had hoped that having been promised
OL,14,Fproper dialogue by MoD ministers that
OL,15,Fwe would see a change of direction.
OL,16,FBut it's the same old MoD up to its
OL,17,Fdirty tricks."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FIn April, families welcomed the Prime
OL,7,FMinister's agreement to meet with them
OL,8,Fas a "significant" step in their quest
OL,9,Ffor "truth, transparency and
OL,10,Faccountability".
OL,12,FMr Cook said the meeting was "more
OL,13,Furgent than ever" and he urged Sir
OL,14,FKeir Starmer to confirm a date "as
OL,15,Fsoon as possible".
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@RO]qD@EOUrD@OO]tD@^OUuD@QO]vD@
OL,26,A`OUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FThe release of the documents has
OL,7,Fprompted renewed demands for full
OL,8,Ftransparency and a judge-led public
OL,9,Finquiry, with families warning they
OL,10,Fhave been informed by senior
OL,11,FGovernment sources that further
OL,12,Fundisclosed material on the crash
OL,13,Fexists across Government in several
OL,14,Flocations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778461395
OL,3,CMoD accused of 'callous disregard' for
OL,4,CChinook families after FOI disclosure
OL,6,FThe Chinook Justice Campaign has
OL,7,Fcalled for a public inquiry and for
OL,8,Fthe case to be treated as one of the
OL,9,Ffirst tests of the proposed
OL,10,FHillsborough Law, which is intended to
OL,11,Fenforce a legal duty of candour on
OL,12,Fpublic authorities.
OL,14,FThe MoD has been approached for
OL,15,Fcomment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
